data.description: Spacious, comfortable and updated only begin to describe this 5 bed 3 bath home located in the Heatherwood subdivision. Location of this property is absolutely perfect as it allows easy access to shopping, downtown, restaurants, schools and parks!   Features inside include an updated kitchen, newer windows, primary on the main level, a fully-finished basement with family room area and loads of storage.   The exterior boasts a fully-fenced backyard, covered back porch with composite decking while the outside of the home was painted in 2021 and new gutters were installed in 2022.  Schedule a showing today with your favorite REALTOR!
